      <para id="id1169644806476"/>
      <para id="id1169642514233">Percy was sad. He walked on and met Old Brown Cow and her little calf.</para>
      <para id="id1169638993061">"Aha!" he said. "Here are some friends to play with me.</para>
      <para id="id1169633364056">I can play with Old Brown Cow.</para>
      <para id="id1169646707913">I can play with the little calf.</para>
      <para id="id6030565">We can play hide-and-seek.</para>
      <para id="id1169634875143">We can play ball.</para>
      <para id="id1169627237316">We can play all kinds of games."</para>
      <para id="id1169637747644">So he crept nearer and said,</para>
