      <para id="id1169640604212">Percy the Porcupine was very, very sad.</para>
      <para id="id1169639092077">Nobody wanted to be his friend.</para>
      <para id="id5876088">Nobody wanted to play with him.</para>
      <para id="id1169635804674">Nobody wanted to play hide-and-seek.</para>
      <para id="id1169632631616">Nobody wanted to play ball.</para>
      <para id="id1169627324200">So he walked back to his berry bush and cried himself to sleep.</para>
      <para id="id1169643244412">And there the porcupines of the forest found him.</para>
      <para id="id3830576">"Percy!" they said, "we will be your friends. We will play with you". And so they did!</para>
